        <updateDate>2021-10-29T13:55:44Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill establishes deadlines for the Bureau of Land Management and the Forest Service to complete the federal permitting and review process with respect to critical mineral production on federal lands. It also establishes related requirements to expedite the process and remove impediments to the production of critical minerals and the mineral security of the United States.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
